    "John Trapp": "Seven days.] To teach the priests to consecrate their whole lives to God\u2019s service.\nVer.\n35. They made.] {See Trapp on \"Ex 32:1\"}\nVer.\nVer. 35. { See Trapp on \"Le 26:34\" }\nVer.\nVer. 35. {See Trapp on \"Le 26:34\"}\nVer."
